dc_title_s: General highway and transportation map, Jasper County, Indiana
dc_description_s: Blue line print. 'Corrected to January 1, 1937.' 'Data obtained from Statewide Highway Planning Survey.' Includes chart 'Culture in unincorporated places' and location map. '37.'
